  be redeclared. src/backend/src/models/types.ts:37-45,93-100;
  .github/copilot-instructions.md:37-40
   - Persistence is an upsert on composite key (user_id, event, channel) and updated_by is
  mandatory, so any write path must always supply full row data.
  src/backend/src/models/preference-repository.ts:6-11,64-77; src/backend/src/db/schema.sql:44-52
   - Notification delivery already has runtime SMS→email fallback behavior in queue handling, but
  that fallback does not mutate stored preferences.
  src/backend/src/services/notification-service.ts:8-17,32-47;
